rComments: J'ai adoré son cours. Un vrai pédagogue et une passion contagieuse pour son métier.
Very passionate about his job. Very demanding but fair. You always know what to expect with him. Loves to tell funny stories.
Great pedagogical approach. Always makes sure you know what to expect from the class and what he expects from you. All in all, a great teacher. And not hard on the eyes either ...
